data.description: Gorgeous 3 bed 2 bath with office in Haughton's Spring Creek Subdivision! This stunning residence offers a fantastic floor plan with functional office space, large laundry room, and custom cabinetry throughout.  Cozy up by the fireplace in the spacious living area with adorned with hardwood floors or unleash your inner chef in the amazing kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances and tons of counter and cabinet space.  Outside, you will enjoy entertaining or enjoying serene evenings by the outdoor fireplace, and the sprinkler system ensures a lush and vibrant lawn year-round. The master suite is a true retreat with a tiled-in shower, oversized whirlpool tub, and a generous walk-in closet. Easy access to I-20 makes living away from the hustle and bustle convenient!
